 intel and counsels him.\nChapter 36: Frank needs to deal with Petrov one on one while Claire tries to preserve the peace-keeping mission. Sacrifices must be made.\n","Title":"House of Cards season three temporarily showed up on Netflix weeks early | The Verge","Tags":["culture","breaking","entertainment"]}